25
00:01:15,320 --> 00:01:18,790
Add that to the pressure of already high unemployment.

26
00:01:18,790 --> 00:01:22,700
So it’s no wonder that Iran has seen more
than 100 public protests

27
00:01:22,700 --> 00:01:24,619
in less than 10 months.

28
00:01:24,619 --> 00:01:26,850
And the protests haven’t eased up.

29
00:01:26,850 --> 00:01:30,180
This next news video is from just after the
Trump administration

30
