53
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:28,780
Yeah!

54
00:02:28,780 --> 00:02:30,740
That’ll fix unemployment!

55
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:34,830
But fear not, where there’s an authoritarian
regime in trouble,

56
00:02:34,830 --> 00:02:37,680
a dictatorship that’s lost the support of
the people,

57
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:40,880
or a system collapsing because of corruption—

58
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:44,300
the Chinese Communist Party will ride to the
rescue.

59
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:47,640
Many traditional buyers of Iranian oil like
South Korea,

60
