oil.

97
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:31,040
Especially since other Chinese oil suppliers
are struggling.

98
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:33,470
And China’s not just getting the oil for
cheap.

99
00:04:33,470 --> 00:04:36,710
